== 各國法律規範 ==
[[國際人道法|國際人道法]]（IHL）嚴格禁止在任何武裝衝突期間的性暴力，[[國際人權法|國際人權法]]（IHRL）和[[國際習慣法|國際習慣法]]則嚴格禁止任何期間的性暴力<ref name="Lindsey 2001 57–61"/><ref name="icrc.org"/><ref name="Physicians for Human Rights 2002"/><ref name="United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs 2007"/>。IHL讓女性得到了雙重保障，除了一般的（與男性同等的）保障以外，還有特別的保障，也就是IHL的保障。根據女性的額外需要而給予她們特別的保護，例如寡婦、傷病患、移民、流離失所者或被拘留者。<ref name="Customary IHL. Rule 134 on Women">{{cite web|title=Customary IHL. Rule 134 on Women|url=http://www.icrc.org/customary-ihl/eng/docs/v1_cha_chapter39_rule134?OpenDocument&highlight=134|publisher=ICRC|accessdate=28 November 2013|archive-date=2015-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150420205607/https://www.icrc.org/customary-ihl/eng/docs/v1_cha_chapter39_rule134?OpenDocument&highlight=134|dead-url=no}}</ref>

盧安達問題國際刑事法庭（ICTR）特設法庭和前南斯拉夫國際刑事法庭（ICTY）做出的突破性[[判例法|判例法]]將強姦和性暴力行為認定為種族滅絕與危害人類罪<ref>{{harvp|Lindsey|2001|pp=57–58}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Bassiouni|first=M. Cherif|title=The Commission of Experts established pursuant to Security Council resolution 780 : Investigating violations of international humanitarian law in the former Yugoslavia|url=https://archive.org/details/commiss_bas_1996_00_0399|year=1996|publisher=International Human Rights Law Institute, DePaul University|location=Chicago, IL|isbn=1-889001-01-5|page=[https://archive.org/details/commiss_bas_1996_00_0399/page/31 31]}}</ref>。ICTR在1998年9月2日將{{link-en|Jean-Paul Akayesu|Jean-Paul Akayesu}}對種族滅絕和危害人類的罪行定為性暴力，這是[[防止及懲治滅絕種族罪公約|防止及懲治滅絕種族罪公約]]通過後首次適用的案子<ref name="unictr.org">{{cite web|title=The Prosecutor v. Jean-Paul Akayesu, Case No. ICTR-96-4-T|url=http://www.unictr.org/Portals/0/Case/English/Akayesu/judgement/akay001.pdf|accessdate=28 November 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130611203452/http://www.unictr.org/Portals/0/Case/English/Akayesu/judgement/akay001.pdf|archive-date=2013-06-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=St-Germain|first1=Tonia|title=Conflict-related sexual violence : international law, local responses|year=2012|publisher=Kumarian Press|location=Sterling, Va.|isbn=978-1-56549-504-3|pages=55–57|last2=Dewey|first2=Susan}}</ref>。而第一起國家違反該公約的判例是ICTY在2007年2月26日判下，塞爾維亞在波士尼亞戰爭中對女性實施有系統的性暴力（強姦營），直接執行了種族滅絕的行為<ref>{{cite web|title=Case information sheet on the Foca Case (Kunarac, Kovac & Vukovic) (IT-96-23 and 23/1)|url=http://www.icty.org/x/cases/kunarac/cis/en/cis_kunarac_al_en.pdf|access-date=2017-02-09|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123192004/https://www.icty.org/x/cases/kunarac/cis/en/cis_kunarac_al_en.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Prosecutor v. Dragoljub Kunarac, Radomir Kovac, and Zoran Vukovic, IT-96-23-T& IT-96-23/1-T|url=http://www.icty.org/x/cases/kunarac/tjug/en/kun-tj010222e.pdf|access-date=2017-02-09|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312195924/https://www.icty.org/x/cases/kunarac/tjug/en/kun-tj010222e.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[國際刑事法院|國際刑事法院]]（ICC）的規約也明確將包括強姦在內的各種性暴力列入[[戰爭罪|戰爭罪]]，並因此承認性暴力是違反IHL和日內瓦公約的罪行。<ref name="Physicians for Human Rights 2002"/><ref>{{cite web|title=Statute of the International Criminal Court (Rome Statute)|url=http://www.icc-cpi.int/NR/rdonlyres/EA9AEFF7-5752-4F84-BE94-0A655EB30E16/0/Rome_Statute_English.pdf|accessdate=28 November 2013|archive-date=2021-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210425051546/https://www.icc-cpi.int/nr/rdonlyres/ea9aeff7-5752-4f84-be94-0a655eb30e16/0/rome_statute_english.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

多不勝數的{{link-en|硬法|Hard law}}和[[軟法|軟法]]文件都定出了保護性犯罪受害者的規則、標準和規範。包括1979年通過、1981年實行的[[消除對婦女一切形式歧視公約|消除對婦女一切形式歧視公約]]（CEDAW）<ref>{{cite web|title=Convention on the Elimination of All Forms of Discrimination against Women (1979), art. 6|url=http://www.un.org/womenwatch/daw/cedaw/text/econvention.htm#article6|accessdate=29 November 2013|archive-date=2014-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326154350/http://www.un.org/womenwatch/daw/cedaw/text/econvention.htm#article6|dead-url=no}}</ref>；1993年決議的[[消除對婦女的暴力行為宣言|消除對婦女的暴力行為宣言]]；1994年的美洲防止，懲罰和根除對婦女暴力行為公約（Inter-American Convention on the Prevention, Punishment and Eradication of Violence Against Women）<ref>{{cite web|title=Inter-American Convention on the Prevention, Punishment and Eradication of Violence Against Women|url=https://www1.umn.edu/humanrts/instree/brazil1994.html|website=University of Minnesota Human Rights Library|accessdate=9 April 2015|archive-date=2016-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604164839/http://www1.umn.edu/humanrts/instree/brazil1994.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；2003年通過的{{link-en|非洲人權憲章與非洲女性人權議定書|The Protocol to the African Charter on Human and Peoples’ Rights on the Rights of Women in Africa}}以及{{link-en|維也納宣言和行動綱領|Vienna Declaration and Programme of Action}}。[[聯合國安全理事會|聯合國安全理事會]]、[[聯合國經濟及社會理事會|聯合國經濟及社會理事會]]、[[聯合國人權委員會|聯合國人權委員會]]對女性的保護並不考慮戰爭或動亂時的特殊性質<ref name="Customary IHL. Rule 134 on Women"/>。[[聯合國秘書長|聯合國秘書長]]的三份報告和[[聯合國安全理事會|聯合國安全理事會]]的五份報告是專門處理性暴力議題的。2009年的{{link-en|聯合國安全理事會第1888號決議|United Nations Security Council Resolution 1888}}特別設立了戰爭中性暴力問題秘書長特別代表辦事處<!--（Office of the Special Representative of the Secretary General for Sexual Violence in Conflict）-->（SRSG-SVC），辦事處列出六個優先事項和八個優先國家：[[波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納|波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納]]、[[中非共和國|中非共和國]]、[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]、[[象牙海岸|象牙海岸]]、[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]、[[賴比瑞亞|賴比瑞亞]]、[[南蘇丹|南蘇丹]]與[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]。另外也從事[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]和[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]的相關事務<ref name="un">{{cite web|title=Office of the Special Representative of the Secretary-General for Sexual Violence in Conflict|url=http://www.un.org/sexualviolenceinconflict/about-us/about-the-office/|accessdate=28 November 2013|archive-date=2018-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181223182401/https://www.un.org/sexualviolenceinconflict/about-us/about-the-office/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年歐洲地區國家推動簽署「伊斯坦堡公約(Istanbul Convention)」責成加入公約的會員國，必須立法對抗各國國內發生的家庭暴力、強迫成婚、盯梢及性暴力。但儘管有這麼多國際法嚴格禁止性暴力，世界各地的許多執法機構仍是績效不彰或形同虛設的。<ref name="Lindsey 2001 57–61"/><ref name="icrc.org"/><ref name="Physicians for Human Rights 2002"/><ref name="United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs 2007"/>

